    "N i converge to T in the flat norm.Proof of Theorem 1.7.",
    "The case k = 0 is Theorem 6.6, the case k = 1 and d ≥ 2 is a special case of Corollary 6.4, the case d ≥ k ≥ 2 is Corollary 6.2.",
